Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装满就可以了  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能再装点  一沓…两沓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支付女儿的手术费需要钱  请不要恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.34,0:00:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮件～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百忙之中打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.75,0:00:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这也是工作啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.60,0:00:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你　你们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.01,0:00:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁寄的死后文
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:01:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人的　女儿寄的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃　那…说是要筹手术费的那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.53,0:01:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.39,0:01:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可悲　难得父亲都去做银行抢劫犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过以未遂结束并自首了　太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后文并无所谓好坏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是继续或者停止

Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}社会科参观　小组决定　五人　一定要男女混合

Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂　你们那边怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一个人　怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四个人也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是老师说要五个人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看这边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟　留级生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真的有趣么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是诅咒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}恨　半死人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是菊川的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.32,0:03:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菊川是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菊川公一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:04:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约半年前被欺负　自杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得　总在网上留言的那人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}半死人：所以　我的名字是半死人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外　还有人从楼梯上摔下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说死去的菊川寄来了信件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后文　好像好几个人都收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能　因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么样了　美川文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然比以前强多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但当我要去帮她时…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总不能一直跟着我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.27,0:04:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确我们年级不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能一直跟着她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往鞋子里放图钉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真老套
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也会被卷进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思　不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃音　你不知道那人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道　谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川煌的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要和她扯上关系比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶　什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一再打扰　真对不住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在图书馆学习到很晚？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正在这　就吃点好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客房服务的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实在的　你为什么不转学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私立之类的　你这么有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不也挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确　虽说是对付媒体策略　还过得起宾馆生活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让我重复几遍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟钱　没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是　因为不想离开美歌负责的投递区？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.83,0:06:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.23,0:06:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:06:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.99,0:07:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“没结束”？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　除此之外不肯再告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“没结束”…什么没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为留级了　还没毕业呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意的话去见她不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行　那样小文就无法自立了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你像那孩子母亲一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你没法自立吧　和她见面的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事　千章
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}海鸥屋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不住　文歌的事全拜托给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事　正所谓找男人不如找女人　找警察不如找平民
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才是　小夏…不　妹妹承蒙你们照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错　说不定会一直承蒙你们照顾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃　是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定啦　说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗　要那小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来　野岛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还没跟别人提过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望她能和我们一起住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁在清扫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教体育的关根和教国语的小山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清不掉的　清不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说一个拿着杖的女孩会送来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是菊川的诅咒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么诅咒　他不是自杀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉对方不就得了　像森下那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒什么的根本就不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被刺了一刀　还被停学了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就跟他扯平了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那是跟森下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是跟菊川吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说得事不关己　你们也是共犯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时　屋顶上不是来了个奇怪的女生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…因此…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外人看来　这学校尽出事故
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到前段时间为止　阿姨也天天念叨要我转学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升三年级了她好像才放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小千和要成了朋友　在这也不全是坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然这儿也不是什么好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么　你果然还没放弃美歌的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干　干嘛突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要揭发假死后文是为了美歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦　不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真不肯死心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,0:10:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站　自立中心前　自立中心前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐　是这儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…嗯　夏香　按按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}停车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自立中心前　下车请小心

Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这叫吴越同舟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}意指与关系不好的人同行、同坐

Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是指敌人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了　别的不说　我们目标相同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相同？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我　我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了美歌吧　是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了　
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我　我是森下俊介
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你肯见我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见过面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然认识　那就好说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那森下知道死后文…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的　说关于死后文的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人　以前也收到过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也是来问菊川的死后文的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…也？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　之前菊川的妹妹来过了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后　问了我很多关于欺负他人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他妹妹关于死后文的事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没把信的真实内容告诉她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为　唯一的哥哥留下的死后文上…只有怨恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会很悲伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个　没办法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是　那位妹妹的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筱崎铃音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筱崎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为父母离婚了　姓氏不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃音？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.07,0:13:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}这是死后文
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦　离婚的话随爸爸妈妈的便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我和哥哥要分开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃音　算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙　不是你哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人　骗了我十多年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么还能和她跟情人生的孩子过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃音　和我们一起住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥　对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起　哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系　铃音　没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.68,0:14:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.31,0:14:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}去死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥　哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我　哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像　喝酒比平时早吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天非常认真工作了　就提早下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.31,0:15:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提早下班？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了　找千章有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}这是死后文　今天晚上11点  3个人一起来　承蒙照顾　特来道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是假的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了吗　就是假的才要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住犯人　好好修理他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是　要是对方是森下那时的那种女生怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次咱们准备周全
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人　我们知道是你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不过是　空罐子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要大声叫啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了　继续走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说　从没听说用电脑打印的死后文
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真正的死后文是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃　那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.02,0:15:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说　我怎么可能知道那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙　自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…这样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从紧急扶梯上来的？　是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…邮递员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写给我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那些家伙不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他们不好　寄些假死后文根本不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…真正的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}不要再做傻事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}菊川公一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊　哥哥并不高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～　找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事　有两个邮递员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是两个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提示　其中一个是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说句　规定邮递员必须带着我们这样的杖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.04,0:18:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边这个有我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的…哎呀　空手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜卡　接得好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是文伽接住的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.74,0:18:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边也是文歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说　你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我们吧　菊川
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算让他们吃了点苦头 以后应该再也不敢欺负人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真苫　谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急措施　没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点和美川汇合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要　我推你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么　为什么要妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后文绝不允许恶意或善意的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然咯　cosplay送假信也不可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂　回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我而言　只有哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过分　太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然骗我　喂　回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我　美川
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.09,0:19:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我也复仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.07,0:19:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道结果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为复仇的恶意　结果我也遭到报应了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于我控诉父亲的恶意的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在学校那所牢笼中　还在服刑中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“还没结束”原来是这个意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才不让我复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不让我遭受恶意的报应
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是　为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你对我施以了善意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.73,0:20:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那点小事…居然做到这一步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止恶意　传播善意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说　文伽　我们是来干嘛的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为被拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们取回衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔这种打扮也不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的　文伽果然很喜欢小文
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:21:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得的小文的善意　想把它传达给铃音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦　不过小文的邮递员打扮好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要脸红啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有多自恋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果死后文到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道　恶作剧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是　中饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃吧　我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.57,0:21:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过不要接近我比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我扯上关系的话　你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我　加入文歌教了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传播善意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌教？　傻死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}一起住怎么样？姐姐也说这样比较好哦　我也很赞成　今天我要去旅店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管闲事

